    <body class="- topic/body " xtrc="body:1;21:11" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">
        <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:1;22:12" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita"> ECOMAPP is a normalized, SKU-driven data model with centralized pricing logic and strong
            referential integrity. The catalog supports 4,824 sellable SKUs derived from 104 base
            product types and 63 style modifiers, designed to be scalable and consistent with
            updates.</p>
        <image class="- topic/image " href="../../../../../../../Downloads/ECOMDB01_ERD.png" id="image_ugv_53r_q3c" placement="inline" xtrc="image:1;26:95" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita"/>
        <section class="- topic/section " id="section_mgk_4rd_q3c" xtrc="section:1;27:43" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">
            <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:2;28:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">Normalization</title>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:2;29:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">ECOMAPP NXTCG demonstrates a strong level of normalization, with the schema largely
                conforming to Third Normal Form (3NF). All relations satisfy the requirements of
                First and Second Normal Forms, and the use of composite‑key tables ensures that each
                non‑key attribute is fully dependent on the entire primary key.</p>
        </section>
        <section class="- topic/section " id="sku-architecture" xtrc="section:2;34:40" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">
            <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:3;35:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">SKU Architecture</title>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:3;36:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">ECOMAPP uses a hierarchical SKU system: <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b " xtrc="b:1;36:59" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">SERIES-STYLE-SERIAL-MODIFIER</b></p>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:4;37:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">Example SKU: <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrc="codeph:1;37:37" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">NAC-SE01-EHM</codeph></p>
            <ul class="- topic/ul " id="ul_lm3_crd_q3c" xtrc="ul:1;38:37" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:1;39:21" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">NA = Series</li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:2;40:21" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita"> S = Style</li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:3;41:21" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">SE01 = Serial Number</li>
                <li class="- topic/li " xtrc="li:4;42:21" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">EHM = Modifier (English, Holofoil, Mint)</li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section class="- topic/section " id="section_anp_fbj_q3c" xtrc="section:3;45:43" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">
            <title class="- topic/title " xtrc="title:4;46:20" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">Pricing Model</title>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:5;47:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">ECOMAPP uses a multiplier-based pricing system where each product variant's final
                price is calculated by multiplying the base price by a modifier-specific
                multiplier.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:6;50:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">The formula is <codeph class="+ topic/ph pr-d/codeph " xtrc="codeph:2;50:39" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">Final Price = BASE_PRICE_CENTS x
                PRICE_MULTIPLIER</codeph>.</p>
            <p class="- topic/p " xtrc="p:7;52:16" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">
                <note class="- topic/note " id="note_lfy_4bj_q3c" xtrc="note:1;53:45" xtrf="file:/C:/Users/jheckel/Documents/Repositories/Spectre/Spectre/docs/Database-Documentation/topics/database-administrator-guide-topic.dita">Users who upload a new product will be able to decipher
                    the price for their product. The pricing model does show the user a recommended
                    price. </note>
            </p>
        </section>
